All Implemented Interfaces:
IFluentCollectionProperty<Owner,Value,Container>, IFluentProperty<Owner,Container>
public class FluentCollectionDelegateProperty<Owner,Value,Container extends Collection<Value>>
extends FluentDelegateProperty<Owner,Container>
implements IFluentCollectionProperty<Owner,Value,Container>

A property with support of fluent interface for collections and ability to delegate a value. Delegation of a value will be triggered each time when fluent interface was used to insert values into collection property.
